name: Fuzzle Puzzles - Play Award-Winning Puzzles in Figma
description:
Enjoy some low carbon footprint entertainment - play award-winning puzzles in Figma!


The puzzles featured in this kit are:

  • Bitten Biscuits designed by Jin-hoo Ahn
  • Cut Trick designed by Vesa Timonen
  • Symmetrick designed by Vesa Timonen
  • Oleo 10 designed by Yuu Asaka.


This Figma kit is made by wentin from Typogram team.


Artboards are set to letter size, you can print and cut it out if you prefer physical form.
